Banazer is the group leader of Banazer Group, which consists of four members, each desiring to advance and expand their respective businesses:

Banazer wants to take a loan for her son who sells mobile calling cards;
Najeba wants to take a loan for her husband who has a general store;
Fareba wants to take a loan for the business of tailoring;
Seema wants to take a loan for her husband who has a carpentry shop. 

They are each very thankful to AFS and Kiva lenders for their support.
